data.description: SpringHaven estates offers the home you've been waiting for, naturally set into Maple Valley's Northeastern corner. This two-story charmer backs up to a green belt with over 140 acres and sits on nearly an acre of its own! Newly finished hardwood floors flow into the kitchen, highlighting the open layout. The lower level has room for everyone while maintaining an intimate setting. Upstairs you find five total bedrooms, separate office space, and a 5 piece bath in the primary suite. Don't miss the walk in closet! Obvious care in every detail of the house unveils multiple upgrades. New Interior/exterior paint, new deck boards, gutters, and over 10k sf of new sod and landscaping are a must see. Located in award-winning Tahoma SD, Welcome Home!
